{"tid":273040,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Wonder Woman 神奇女俠電影彩蛋與參考","createTime":"2017-06-06T09:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T07:38:03.000Z","uid":121471,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"48d82fce520ef72ef55ad1cd988e21cbe14375f3","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:12:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://screenrant.com/wonder-woman-movie-easter-eggs-comic-2017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscreenrant.com%2Fwonder-woman-movie-easter-eggs-comic-2017%2F&d=mkcDfsIFss0oIR5MJ5PkvMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=337edd1a\" target=\"_blank\">http://screenrant.com/wonder-woman-movie-easter-eggs-comic-2017/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://comicbook.com/dc/2017/06/02/easter-eggs-and-dc-comics-references-in-wonder-woman/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcomicbook.com%2Fdc%2F2017%2F06%2F02%2Feaster-eggs-and-dc-comics-references-in-wonder-woman%2F&d=mkcDfsIFss0oIR5MJ5PkvMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=32a74d72\" target=\"_blank\">http://comicbook.com/dc/2017/06/02/easter-eggs-and-dc-comics-references-in-wonder-woman/</a><br />\nWW對比返DCEU之前三套戲黎講Easter Eggs同References都係比較少.<br />\n不過少極都有可以講下既地方.<br />\n我膽粗粗試下根據外國網站既資料分享下主要同WW有關既彩蛋.<br />\n如有出錯請幫忙指正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/T5DxIa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FT5DxIa.jpg&h=367e4b2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一個應該就係人都會明白<br />\n套戲一開始見到架車寫住Wayne Security, 之後Diana就收到佢100年前張相.<br />\n就係BVS入面Bruce喺腦搵到果張, 宜家直頭有埋實物連同Bruce留言送返俾Diana.<br />\n套戲最尾亦見到Diana回email俾Bruce道謝.<br />\n(電影Art book都幾有心思整左張相既膠片連埋信封)"},{"pid":"78190effce05480dde3cdb4e881255e9930ad959","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/FTULS3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FFTULS3.jpg&h=715f7dc6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/y5JFfq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fy5JFfq.jpg&h=c7938572&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影童年Diana聽Hippolyta講關於Amazon歷史既故事.<br />\n講到Amazon由眾神創造時出現一班女人由水中走出黎既畫面.<br />\n就係參考返87年WW漫畫Reboot後由George perez寫既起源故事.<br />\n漫畫話Amazon由Demeter, Aphrodite, Athena, Artemis同Hestia所創造.<br />\n電影簡單一句眾神."},{"pid":"48dd358ce01510269b364a732727bdfded2372b8","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/p3lKnG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fp3lKnG.jpg&h=cc961cbc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/eK62p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FeK62p3.jpg&h=9badd304&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/aXtP9I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FaXtP9I.jpg&h=3405caf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影Amazon歷史故事講到佢地受奴役, 再由Hippolyta解放.<br />\n除左參考87年故事外, 其實亦係41年最初既起源故事.<br />\n漫畫故事其實由女神Aphrodite(87年係Athena)先救Hippolyta, 再由佢帶領其他Amazon解放."},{"pid":"e2f6785ec8ef8606ebc97e7b8a8b843d36e22b99","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/L76ZdF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FL76ZdF.jpg&h=59aa9661&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/NnLE7s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FNnLE7s.jpg&h=d4feb30f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影入面其中一個比較突出既Amazon, 本身唔係演員<br />\n而係Boxer冠軍Ann Wolfe.<br />\n佢所扮演既角色雖然戲入面冇提過名, 但係根據導演所講,<br />\n其實佢就係一個漫畫迷唔會陌生既角色, Artemis.<br />\n(估唔到電影會咁唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )"},{"pid":"474b8ca633c8df1411134d0ac2788db0a188086d","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:15:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/xgJe16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FxgJe16.jpg&h=5b44c7fc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/9FEoGn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F9FEoGn.jpg&h=396b2e66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影中Diana由水中救返Steve後, 同Steve講佢身在Themyscira.<br />\nThemyscira一詞其實係87年Reboot先開始成為Amazon居住地既名稱<br />\n由41年一開始已經用Paradise island.<br />\n電影中Hippolyta同童年Diana講神俾左個天堂佢地.<br />\n而男女主角跳舞之前Steve亦用Paradise island黎形容Themyscira."},{"pid":"2c2982703e6660d2fe7bdb2060da92ec3422e587","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:16:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/OujlCG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FOujlCG.jpg&h=054b81a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/e46H8n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fe46H8n.jpg&h=87719fd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影中Steve俾Lasso of truth套住將所有野講晒出黎.<br />\n但係Diana將呢件WW招牌武器叫做Lasso of Hestia.<br />\n其實87年漫畫reboot, Lasso係由過女神Hestia賜予令人講出真話既力量"},{"pid":"9a0c124fa6e3cc725c0af8938e38be9c84e3a933","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/E5qZIK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FE5qZIK.jpg&h=25cc7e5f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/gG65lI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FgG65lI.jpg&h=6b430c8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影聲稱可以殺神但只係把廢劍既God killer.<br />\n出自漫畫New 52<br />\n詳情可睇<a href=\"http://www.cbr.com/wonder-woman-movie-god-killer-sword-explained/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbr.com%2Fwonder-woman-movie-god-killer-sword-explained%2F&d=mkcDfsIFss0oIR5MJ5PkvMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=c0ca83a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cbr.com/wonder-woman-movie-god-killer-sword-explained/</a>"},{"pid":"ebfe30a1bffbe64ae2f9f2a6f9fec583c50e75fc","tid":273040,"uid":18818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:18:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://screenrant.com/wonder-woman-movie-easter-eggs-comic-2017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscreenrant.com%2Fwonder-woman-movie-easter-eggs-comic-2017%2F&d=mkcDfsIFss0oIR5MJ5PkvMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=337edd1a\" target=\"_blank\">http://screenrant.com/wonder-woman-movie-easter-eggs-comic-2017/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://comicbook.com/dc/2017/06/02/easter-eggs-and-dc-comics-references-in-wonder-woman/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcomicbook.com%2Fdc%2F2017%2F06%2F02%2Feaster-eggs-and-dc-comics-references-in-wonder-woman%2F&d=mkcDfsIFss0oIR5MJ5PkvMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=32a74d72\" target=\"_blank\">http://comicbook.com/dc/2017/06/02/easter-eggs-and-dc-comics-references-in-wonder-woman/</a><br />\nWW對比返DCEU之前三套戲黎講Easter Eggs同References都係比較少.<br />\n不過少極都有可以講下既地方.<br />\n我膽粗粗試下根據外國網站既資料分享下主要同WW有關既彩蛋.<br />\n如有出錯請幫忙指正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/T5DxIa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FT5DxIa.jpg&h=367e4b2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一個應該就係人都會明白<br />\n套戲一開始見到架車寫住Wayne Security, 之後Diana就收到佢100年前張相.<br />\n就係BVS入面Bruce喺腦搵到果張, 宜家直頭有埋實物連同Bruce留言送返俾Diana.<br />\n套戲最尾亦見到Diana回email俾Bruce道謝.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(電影Art book都幾有心思整左張相既膠片連埋信封)</span></blockquote><br />\nart book送？"},{"pid":"0d7d104200c0eb517844459cfd831894c4b118c5","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:19:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/F9kQbo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FF9kQbo.jpg&h=542d487a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/8oVIK9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F8oVIK9.jpg&h=ade5ce1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影中Diana去到倫敦後被Steve帶去買衫.<br />\n不停試左好多款, 根據Etta所講最後一款係outfit #226.<br />\n呢個數字正正就係87年漫畫reboot後直到06年最後一期既期數."},{"pid":"53fbae29423586b6862cccb203984df2b1fae92b","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/6goWEu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F6goWEu.jpg&h=8dbf7ca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影中Diana介紹自己時俾Steve打斷而變成Diana Prince.<br />\n之後Steve更加話Diana係佢秘書.<br />\n41年漫畫中Diana Prince其實係一個護士, Diana&amp;#25886;左佢個身份成為護士及後再成為Steve上司秘書."},{"pid":"9266e70abbccda68d76f64bda860817f6a69d983","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/poySat.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FpoySat.jpg&h=cac439eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/nm0zXg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2Fnm0zXg.jpg&h=06f5422f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影中Diana第一次感受到雪糕既美味後更讚賞賣雪糕條友應該感到自豪.<br />\n其實出自漫畫New 52既Justice League."},{"pid":"73cfad31f9892697258da434aded172b42dbb1af","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/Y2wdV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FY2wdV7.jpg&h=69e0f946&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影中Ares同Diana講佢真係真理之神.<br />\n漫畫中Ares的確講過War is truth.<br />\n(所以我一直奇怪點解尾片credit嗚謝漫畫作者冇Gail Simone.)<br />\n漫畫中Diana亦短暫做過真理之神Goddess of truth"},{"pid":"8b2853baf172905f0d56d38a75f419539d451fca","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:24:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/Od4eCI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FOd4eCI.jpg&h=51a1efe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAres同Diana講出真相佢其實係Zeus個女.<br />\n出自漫畫New 52既WW."},{"pid":"d8b416e8f05a218fcdb44766ab4a335327ffa77b","tid":273040,"uid":7123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:26:11.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇完<br />\n諸神係咪死剩Diana 1個🤔"},{"pid":"115e2785badf186f85b8511c1e855d3158e0587a","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:26:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/pFyzrn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FpFyzrn.jpg&h=8422a3cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/Gaj4ex.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FGaj4ex.jpg&h=5793f802&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/8giGIh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F8giGIh.jpg&h=b9c8ec55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影最後Diana用對Bracelets將電打爆Ares.<br />\n其實亦係黎自Gail Simone既WW漫畫.<br />\n漫畫入面直情可以召雷, 仲要係Zeus俾既能力.<br />\n(註: 當時並唔係Zeus個女. 對Bracelets材料係Zeus個盾所以有埋放電能力)"},{"pid":"1c6945f2c1fd7e8e57ab8c2a7f33de1d1a882fa3","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:27:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/H1UnBm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FH1UnBm.jpg&h=8bf70e45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影WW雙手反坦克<br />\n漫畫最出名就係Alex ross大師既WW:Spirit of Truth一幕"},{"pid":"7825f5a80e5b7ec8254b492a5227e98a62f47ec2","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/xWzuSi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FxWzuSi.jpg&h=be3a7344&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/3189lo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F3189lo.jpg&h=1e54d520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影Diana擋子彈救Steve一幕<br />\n就係向78年超人電影入面Clark接子彈救Lois致敬<br />\n有趣既係兩套戲入面Steve同Lois都係有勇無謀咁出手，如果冇Diana同Clark都好大機會中左槍"},{"pid":"24936fe4209066b36ccf0ef4cd53dbaac31a33b5","tid":273040,"uid":50613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/H1UnBm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FH1UnBm.jpg&h=8bf70e45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n電影WW雙手反坦克<br />\n漫畫最出名就係Alex ross大師既WW:Spirit of Truth一幕</blockquote><br />\n屌成日想買返幅Alex Ross掛係屋企但係好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9238e5f435c072bff51f523f254267e57ea3556","tid":273040,"uid":50613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:37:02.000Z","msg":"btw留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24e1686ada36df4d0751d6cb57533c8f90fa378","tid":273040,"uid":35166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:37:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a10be49979e1f67f9ca2f4ceec2f3dbca8f447b","tid":273040,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:44:15.000Z","msg":"小智巴個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b4552e5c6a2ac1a17a5d427d61f40df850fe22","tid":273040,"uid":34123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:47:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=VI&amp;message=6732653&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DVI%26message%3D6732653%26page%3D1&d=mkcDfsIFss0oIR5MJ5PkvMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=f9d849ab\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=VI&amp;message=67326