 />\n(hippolyta好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n同埋rebirth入面都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe8ba4ac8fcaac57cde682142023f7a96867b203","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://screenrant.com/wonder-woman-movie-easter-eggs-comic-2017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscreenrant.com%2Fwonder-woman-movie-easter-eggs-comic-2017%2F&d=mkcDfsIFss0oIR5MJ5PkvMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=337edd1a\" target=\"_blank\">http://screenrant.com/wonder-woman-movie-easter-eggs-comic-2017/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://comicbook.com/dc/2017/06/02/easter-eggs-and-dc-comics-references-in-wonder-woman/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcomicbook.com%2Fdc%2F2017%2F06%2F02%2Feaster-eggs-and-dc-comics-references-in-wonder-woman%2F&d=mkcDfsIFss0oIR5MJ5PkvMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=32a74d72\" target=\"_blank\">http://comicbook.com/dc/2017/06/02/easter-eggs-and-dc-comics-references-in-wonder-woman/</a><br />\nWW對比返DCEU之前三套戲黎講Easter Eggs同References都係比較少.<br />\n不過少極都有可以講下既地方.<br />\n我膽粗粗試下根據外國網站既資料分享下主要同WW有關既彩蛋.<br />\n如有出錯請幫忙指正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/T5DxIa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FT5DxIa.jpg&h=367e4b2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一個應該就係人都會明白<br />\n套戲一開始見到架車寫住Wayne Security, 之後Diana就收到佢100年前張相.<br />\n就係BVS入面Bruce喺腦搵到果張, 宜家直頭有埋實物連同Bruce留言送返俾Diana.<br />\n套戲最尾亦見到Diana回email俾Bruce道謝.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(電影Art book都幾有心思整左張相既膠片連埋信封)</span></blockquote><br />\nart book送？</blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"6fa086f855f54008b08d1bf15593c8abbd1defbf","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T11:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;img src=&quot;<a href=\"https://upload.cc/i2/L76ZdF.jpg&quot;\" da