角色雖然戲入面冇提過名, 但係根據導演所講,<br />\n其實佢就係一個漫畫迷唔會陌生既角色, Artemis.<br />\n(估唔到電影會咁唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )</blockquote><br />\n好鍾意佢繼承做wonder woman個故事<br />\n(hippolyta好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n同埋rebirth入面都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔怪得Hippolyta既，唔想自己個女有事好正常<br />\n但係之後因為<span style=\"color: red;\">咁Diana真係死左先過癮</span><br />\nHippolyta最仆街係做過WW後就上左癮</blockquote><br />\n就係因為hippolyta使橫手 最後都係累死diana<br />\n個故事咁先好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95638329fd337e770329e8db63b35def124d7b8","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:17:38.000Z","msg":"但係繼jimmy Olsen後又一個角色俾DCEU浪費左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3baac97859ac535a1a4b7449452a672b2bf467","tid":273040,"uid":33864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:46:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係繼jimmy Olsen後又一個角色俾DCEU浪費左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n電影就未必會拍到咁遠 所以冇乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d122ae64707f511291e3539bc6e91255435b11d","tid":273040,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:52:28.000Z","msg":"仲話唔係前輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd31f743e58b31e4099b88b4300d70d01c86841","tid":273040,"uid":121471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T14:55:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲話唔係前輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"